<figureCitation id="06986A80C6E2FF132BA59E53311D7878" box="[430,527,257,281]" captionStart="FIGURES 711–720" captionStartId="160.[151,264,1473,1495]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,409,1452]" captionTargetId="figure@160.[151,1436,409,1452]" captionTargetPageId="160" captionText="FIGURES 711–720. Female epigyna in ventral views and cleared female genitalia in dorsal views, Carapoia agilis group and unplaced species. 711–712. Carapoia exigua sp. n., from Morro de Pedra (UFMG 21557). 713–714. C. djavani sp. n., from Pedra Talhada (ZFMK Ar 19292). 715–716. C. agilis sp. n., from near Bonito (ZFMK Ar 19295). 717, 720. C. bispina sp. n., from near Bonito (ZFMK Ar 19300). 718–719.C. maculata sp. n., from Morro de Pedra (ZFMK Ar 19299)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1202693/files/figure.png" pageId="150" pageNumber="151">711–712</figureCitation>
